  m_Name: NeighborJournal_04
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 21
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #4 \u2014 C\xF4 gi\xE1o Lan"
  category: 3
  content: "Ng\xE0y 14 th\xE1ng 3. H\xF4m nay l\xE0 ng\xE0y cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng t\xF4i
    \u0111\u1EE9ng tr\xEAn b\u1EE5c gi\u1EA3ng. L\u0169 tr\u1EBB ho\u1EA3ng s\u1EE3,
    ph\u1EE5 huynh g\u1ECDi \u0111i\u1EC7n li\xEAn t\u1EE5c h\u1ECFi khi n\xE0o m\u1EDF
    l\u1EA1i tr\u01B0\u1EDDng. Hi\u1EC7u tr\u01B0\u1EDFng b\u1EA3o t\u1EA1m \u0111\xF3ng
    c\u1EEDa hai tu\u1EA7n. Hai tu\u1EA7n... ai c\u0169ng n\xF3i hai tu\u1EA7n. T\xF4i
    \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i cu\u1ED1n nh\u1EADt k\xFD n\xE0y trong ng\u0103n b\xE0n,
    ph\xF2ng khi c\xF3 ai quay l\u1EA1i. C\xE1c em h\u1ECDc tr\xF2 c\u1EE7a t\xF4i,
    c\xF4 xin l\u1ED7i v\xEC \u0111\xE3 kh\xF4ng b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    c\xE1c em."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
